---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../styles/main.css';
import '../styles/sub-pages.css';
---

<Base
  title="Impeccable：给 AI 编程工具补上的设计升级"
  description="1 个核心 skill、23 个命令，以及精选反模式，帮助 AI 产出更有判断的前端设计。支持 Cursor、Claude Code、Gemini CLI 与 Codex CLI。"
  activeNav="home"
  canonicalPath="/"
  mainId="main-content"
  mainClass="site-content"
  ogTitle="Impeccable：面向 AI 编程工具的设计技能包"
  ogDescription="1 个核心 skill、23 个命令，以及精选反模式，帮助 AI 产出更有判断的前端设计。"
  ogImage="https://impeccable.style/og-image.jpg"
  twitterSite="@pbakaus"
  twitterCreator="@pbakaus"
>

<Fragment slot="head">
  <script is:inline async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-TEXGHC7V34"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());
    gtag('config', 'G-TEXGHC7V34');
  </script>
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
</Fragment>

<Fragment slot="before-header">
  <div class="grain-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</Fragment>

<Fragment slot="after-header">
  <!-- Sticky Section Nav -->
  <nav class="section-nav" id="section-nav" aria-label="页面章节">
    <a href="#foundation" class="section-nav-item" data-section="foundation"><span class="section-nav-num">01</span><span class="section-nav-label">基础</span></a>
    <a href="#language" class="section-nav-item" data-section="language"><span class="section-nav-num">02</span><span class="section-nav-label">语言</span></a>
    <a href="#why" class="section-nav-item" data-section="why"><span class="section-nav-num">03</span><span class="section-nav-label">案例</span></a>
    <a href="#live-mode" class="section-nav-item" data-section="live-mode"><span class="section-nav-num">04</span><span class="section-nav-label">实时</span></a>
    <a href="#downloads" class="section-nav-item" data-section="downloads"><span class="section-nav-num">05</span><span class="section-nav-label">安装</span></a>
    <a href="#changelog" class="section-nav-item" data-section="changelog"><span class="section-nav-num">06</span><span class="section-nav-label">更新</span></a>
    <a href="#faq" class="section-nav-item" data-section="faq"><span class="section-nav-num">07</span><span class="section-nav-label">问答</span></a>
  </nav>

  <!-- 1. HERO - Combined with Problem Section -->
  <section id="hero" class="hero-combined">
    <div class="hero-combined-container">
      <!-- Left: Title & Info -->















      <div class="hero-combined-left">
      <h1 class="hero-title-combined">Impeccable</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline-combined">给 AI 编程工具补上设计表达能力</p>

      <p class="hero-hook-text hero-hook-text--full">真正好的设计提示词，背后需要足够精确的设计语言。大多数人没有这套词汇。Impeccable 会把深层设计知识交给你的 AI，并提供 23 个命令来精准引导结果。</p>
      <p class="hero-hook-text hero-hook-text--short">Impeccable 让你的 AI 学会真正的设计，并给你 23 个命令来引导结果。</p>

      <div class="hero-included-box">
      <span class="hero-included-title">包含内容</span>
      <div class="hero-included-items">
      <span>一个带 23 个设计命令的 <em>Impeccable</em> agent skill</span>
      <span class="hero-included-sep">·</span>
      <span>可选 CLI + Chrome 扩展</span>
      </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-cta-group">
      <a href="#downloads" class="hero-cta-combined">立即开始</a>


      <div class="hero-logos-inline">
      <span class="hero-logos-label">支持</span>
      <div class="hero-logos-row">
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Cursor"><img src="assets/cursor-logo.png" alt="Cursor" width="24" height="24" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Claude Code"><img src="assets/claude-logo.png" alt="Claude Code" width="24" height="24" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Gemini CLI"><img src="assets/gemini-logo.png" alt="Gemini CLI" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Codex CLI"><img src="assets/openai-logo.png" alt="Codex CLI" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="VS Code Copilot"><img src="assets/github-logo.png" alt="VS Code Copilot" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Antigravity"><img src="assets/antigravity-logo.png" alt="Antigravity" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Kiro"><img src="assets/kiro-logo.png" alt="Kiro" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="OpenCode"><img src="assets/opencode-logo.png" alt="OpenCode" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy"></span>
      <span class="hero-logo-icon has-tooltip" data-tooltip="Pi"><img src="assets/pi-logo.svg" alt="Pi" width="20" height="20" loading="lazy" style="background:#1a1a1a;border-radius:50%;padding:3px"></span>
      </div>
      </div>


      </div>
      <p class="hero-version-link"><a href="#changelog">v3.0.7：新增 italic-serif hero 与 eyebrow chip 检测，live session 支持断线恢复</a></p>
      </div>
















      <!-- Right: Before/After Demo -->
      <div class="hero-combined-right">
        <div class="split-comparison" id="lens-comparison">
          <div class="split-container">
            <!-- Before: AI Slop -->
            <div class="split-before">
              <span class="split-badge split-badge--before">改造前</span>
              <div class="slop-card">
                <div class="slop-header">
                  <div class="slop-avatar"></div>
                  <div class="slop-text">
                    <div class="slop-title">欢迎来到我们的平台</div>
                    <div class="slop-subtitle">满足你一切需求的最佳方案</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="slop-body">这是一段毫无信息量的占位文案，看起来哪里都能用，也因此哪都不对。</p>
                <button class="slop-button">立即开始</button>
              </div>
              <!-- Callout labels pointing to issues -->
              <div class="slop-callouts">
                <span class="slop-callout" data-point="font">Inter 字体</span>
                <span class="slop-callout" data-point="gradient">紫色渐变</span>
                <span class="slop-callout" data-point="copy">泛化文案</span>
                <span class="slop-callout" data-point="rounded">卡片套卡片</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- After: Impeccable (shown through split) -->
            <div class="split-after">
              <span class="split-badge split-badge--after">改造后</span>
              <div class="impeccable-card">
                <p class="impeccable-eyebrow">设计升级</p>
                <p class="impeccable-title">有判断的界面</p>
                <p class="impeccable-body">每个元素都有理由存在，层级自然引导视线，留白也真正参与表达。</p>
                <button class="impeccable-button">继续查看</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- The Divider -->
            <div class="split-divider"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="split-labels">
            <div class="split-label-item" data-point="before">
              <span class="split-label-dot"></span>
              <span>普通 AI 输出</span>
            </div>
            <div class="split-label-item" data-point="after">
              <span class="split-label-dot split-label-dot--accent"></span>
              <span>叠加设计技能</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Fragment>


    <!-- 01. THE FOUNDATION - Design knowledge -->
    <section class="foundation-section" id="foundation">
      <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
        <span class="section-number">01</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">基础能力</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="foundation-content">
        <p class="section-lead" data-reveal>在任何命令运行之前，Impeccable 会先让你的 AI 学会真正的设计。7 份参考文件会在每次提示里一起加载：排版、色彩、动效、空间、交互、响应式与 UX 文案。</p>

        <div class="foundation-grid" data-reveal>
          <!-- 7 dimension cards, rendered by JS -->
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-cta" data-reveal>
          <p class="foundation-cta-text">先运行一次 <code><span class="foundation-slash">/</span>impeccable teach</code>，把项目的设计上下文建立起来。之后每个命令都会受益。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 02. THE LANGUAGE - Commands vocabulary + demos -->
    <section class="language-section" id="language">
      <div id="solution" style="height:0;overflow:hidden;visibility:hidden"></div>
      <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
        <span class="section-number">02</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">设计语言</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="language-content">
        <div class="language-intro-row" data-reveal>
          <p class="section-lead">23 个命令构成了你和 AI 之间共享的设计词汇表。每个命令都对应一个明确学科：<code>/typeset</code> 负责排版，<code>/colorize</code> 负责色彩，<code>/animate</code> 负责动效。你可以直接说出想调整的那一件事，而不必绕着解释。任选一个看看它如何工作，或 <a href="/docs" class="cheatsheet-link">浏览完整参考 &rarr;</a></p>
          <div class="language-view-toggle" role="tablist" aria-label="命令视图">
            <button type="button" role="tab" class="language-view-tab is-active" data-view="palette" aria-selected="true">画廊</button>
            <button type="button" role="tab" class="language-view-tab" data-view="periodic" aria-selected="false">图谱</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="commands-section" style="height:0;overflow:hidden;visibility:hidden"></div>

        <div class="language-view language-view--palette is-active" data-view-panel="palette">
          <div class="commands-subsection">
            <div class="commands-gallery">
              <!-- Rendered by JS -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="language-view language-view--periodic" data-view-panel="periodic" hidden>
          <div class="solution-visual-interactive" id="framework-viz-container" data-reveal>
          <!-- Periodic table generated by JS -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 04. WHY IMPECCABLE - Feature loop -->
    <section class="why-section" id="why">
      <div class="why-content" data-reveal>
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-number">03</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">实际价值</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="why-layout">
          <div class="why-left">
            <ol class="why-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Impeccable 的核心价值">
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab is-active" data-index="vz" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="why-panel-vz"><span class="why-tab-num">01</span><span class="why-tab-label">先可视化，再交付</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="0" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-0"><span class="why-tab-num">02</span><span class="why-tab-label">有上下文的设计</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="1" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-1"><span class="why-tab-num">03</span><span class="why-tab-label">阻断 AI slop</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="2" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-2"><span class="why-tab-num">04</span><span class="why-tab-label">扎进真实代码库</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="3" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-3"><span class="why-tab-num">05</span><span class="why-tab-label">品牌和产品分开处理</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="4" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-4"><span class="why-tab-num">06</span><span class="why-tab-label">直接在代码里设计</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="5" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-5"><span class="why-tab-num">07</span><span class="why-tab-label">把 DESIGN.md 带着走</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="6" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-6"><span class="why-tab-num">08</span><span class="why-tab-label">适合 CI/CD</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            <li><button role="tab" class="why-tab" data-index="7" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="why-panel-7"><span class="why-tab-num">09</span><span class="why-tab-label">Chrome 扩展</span><span class="why-tab-progress" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="why-panels">
            <article class="why-panel" id="why-panel-0" role="tabpanel" data-index="0" hidden>
              <h3 class="why-panel-title">先知道在为谁设计。</h3>
              <p class="why-panel-body">大多数 AI 工具只能一枪打一张看起来像样的 mock。Impeccable 则从一段对话开始：受众是谁、品牌个性如何、哪些方向明确不要、审美该往哪里走。它会把答案写进 <code>PRODUCT.md</code> 与 <code>DESIGN.md</code>，每次执行命令前都先读取。结果不再只是某个行业的通用印象，而是更贴近真实业务的设计。</p>
              <div class="why-visual why-visual--productmd">
                <div class="why-productmd-file">
                  <div class="why-productmd-header">
                    <span class="why-productmd-filename">PRODUCT.md</span>
                    <span class="why-productmd-status">每个命令都会读取</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="why-productmd-body">
                    <div class="why-productmd-field">
                      <span class="why-productmd-k">用户</span>
                      <span class="why-productmd-v">值班中的 SRE，阅读速度快，经常在光线昏暗环境下查看。</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-productmd-field">
                      <span class="why-productmd-k">Register</span>
                      <span class="why-productmd-v">Product。设计服务于任务本身。</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-productmd-field">
                      <span class="why-productmd-k">品牌语气</span>
                      <span class="why-productmd-v">冷静、克制、无夸张营销腔。</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="why-productmd-field">
                      <span class="why-productmd-k">反参考</span>
                      <span class="why-productmd-v">紫色渐变、玻璃拟态、“提升你的生产力”这类套话。</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <aside class="why-productmd-commands">
                  <span class="why-productmd-commands-label">命令</span>
                  <code>/impeccable teach</code>
                  <code>/impeccable document</code>
                  <code>/impeccable shape</code>
                </aside>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="why-panel why-panel--vizfirst is-active" id="why-panel-vz" role="tabpanel" data-index="vz">
              <h3 class="why-panel-title">先看见它，再把它上线。</h3>
              <p class="why-panel-body">Neo Mirai 一开始只是几张生成式参考图：一套品牌工具板和一张高保真大会页面 mock。<code>/impeccable craft</code> 把它们变成了真正可响应的网站，再在浏览器里继续迭代，直到线上页面和最初方向对齐为止。</p>
              <div class="why-visual why-visual--vizfirst">
                <figure class="why-vz-plate why-vz-plate--hifi">
                  <span class="why-vz-plate-kind">01 &middot; 可视化</span>
                  <a class="why-vz-plate-frame" href="/cases/neo-mirai" aria-label="阅读 Neo Mirai 案例">
                    <img src="assets/openai_image_2_hifi.jpg" alt="自动生成的高保真落地页参考图，采用温暖纸感的编辑风格。" loading="lazy" width="864" height="1821" />
                  </a>
                </figure>
                <figure class="why-vz-plate why-vz-plate--brand">
                  <span class="why-vz-plate-kind">02 &middot; 塑形</span>
                  <a class="why-vz-plate-frame" href="/cases/neo-mirai" aria-label="阅读 Neo Mirai 案例">
                    <img src="assets/openai_image_2_brand.jpg" alt="自动生成的品牌工具板：虚构 AI 设计大会的标识、配色、字体、图标系统与应用示意。" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
                  </a>
                </figure>
                <figure class="why-vz-plate why-vz-plate--live">
                  <span class="why-vz-plate-kind">03 &middot; 实时构建</span>
                  <a class="why-vz-plate-frame" href="/neo-mirai/" aria-label="打开 Neo Mirai 线上版本">
                    <img src="assets/cases/neo-mirai/live-fold.png" alt="根据生成式大会参考图实现完成的 Neo Mirai 网站首页与议程区块。" loading="lazy" width="1440" height="1100" />
                  </a>
                </figure>
              </div>
              <p class="why-panel-meta">一张生成式参考最终落成已上线的 HTML、CSS、资产、响应式修正与交互打磨。&middot; <a href="/cases/neo-mirai">阅读案例 &rarr;</a> &middot; <a href="/neo-mirai/">打开线上版本 &rarr;</a></p>
            </article>

            <article class="why-panel why-panel--antidote" id="why-panel-1" role="tabpanel" data-index="1" hidden>
              <h3 class="why-panel-title">所有模型都从同一批 slop 里学过来。</h3>
              <p class="why-panel-body">没有干预时，它们会反复产出同一种错误：紫色渐变、卡片套卡片、渐变文字、低对比度标签。Impeccable 给其中 25 条起了明确名字，能在代码和浏览器里直接检测，并把这些坏习惯反过来教给 AI 去避开。</p>
              <div class="why-visual why-visual--antidote">
                <div class="patterns-tabbed" id="patterns-categories">
                  <!-- Rendered by app.js from /api/patterns -->
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-stack-container">
                  <div class="gallery-stack-header">
                    <h4 class="gallery-stack-title">反面案例集</h4>
                    <button class="gallery-stack-btn gallery-stack-prev" aria-label="上一张">&larr;</button>
                    <button class="gallery-stack-btn gallery-stack-next" aria-label="下一张">&rarr;</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="gallery-stack" id="gallery-stack">
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/purple-gradients.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/purple-gradients.png" alt="紫色渐变界面" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">紫色渐变</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/thick-border-cards.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/thick-border-cards.png" alt="厚边强调卡片" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">侧条卡片</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/cardocalypse.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/cardocalypse.png" alt="卡片套卡片" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">Cardocalypse</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/inter-everywhere.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/inter-everywhere.png" alt="到处都是 Inter 字体" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">Inter 到处都是</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/layout-templates.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/layout-templates.png" alt="模板式布局" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">模板式布局</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/antipattern-examples/bad-contrast.html" class="gallery-stack-card">
                      <img src="antipattern-images/bad-contrast.png" alt="低对比度文本" loading="lazy">
                      <span class="gallery-stack-label">糟糕对比度</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                  <a class="gallery-stack-link" href="/slop">查看完整目录 &rarr;</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="why-panel" id="why-panel-2" role="tabpanel" data-index="2" hidden>
              <h3 class="why-panel-title">它就是为真实生产代码库准备的。</h3>
              <p class="why-panel-body">Impeccable 会读取你现有的 tokens、组件和渲染结果。它打磨已有内容、指出回归问题，并且始终待在你的设计系统内部工作，而不是每次都凭空发明一套新的视觉体系。</p>
              <div class="why-visual why-visual--terminal">
                <div class="why-terminal">
                  <div class="why-terminal-header">
                    <span class="why-terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="why-terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="why-terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="why-terminal-title">/impeccable polish：扫描代码库</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="why-terminal-body">
                    <div class="why-terminal-line why-terminal-line--prompt"><span class="why-terminal-prompt">&rsaquo;</span> 正在遍历 src/…</div>
                    <div class="why-terminal-line">  <span class="why-terminal-ok">&check;</span> <span class="why-terminal-path">src/styles/tokens.css</span> &nbsp;<span class="why-terminal-meta">14 colors, 6 font sizes, 7 spacing steps</span></div>
